  <brief_title>The Role of Clinical Pharmacist in Management of DDIs in CHF Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Clinical Pharmacist's Intervention in Management of Clinically Relevant Drug-drug Interactions in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure</official_title>
  <sponsors>
