  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To assess the difference in frequency and severity of clinically significant DDIs in control arm and interventional arm between admission and discharge</measure>
    <time_frame>90 days</time_frame>
    <description>We will measure the difference in clinically significant DDIs between admission and discharge. The doctors in control group will not receive the advice about DDIs between drugs prescribed to patient, while the doctors in interventional group will. With this will will assess the impact of the advice in the occurence of DDIs between admission and discharge for both groups.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
